    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Residents of Prosser are jubilant\nover the news from Washington\nthat the secretary of the interior\nhas approved the Teton and Sun\nnyside irrigation projects. The\nSunnyside project carries with it\nthe purchase of the Sunnyside can\nal, directly tributary to Prosser, be-\nsides the irrigation of much new\nland in that vicinity."
    }
